name: MD File Reader
synccode: <div><div><div><div><div><div>on ➢❲[text]❳ {⟪</div><div>if (re.search (r'%5C.md$', message.data)):</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; f = open (message.data, 'r')</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; result = f.read ()</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; self.send (self, 'text', result, message)</div><div>else:</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; self.send (self, 'text', '', message)</div><div>⟫}</div></div></div></div></div></div><div><br></div>
